quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,26,"GomЙ—ii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e fewjiino, Alla yirbiniri mahdeele maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka doose. Kippoodi ndin yanti e maЙ“Й“e, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e nokku ka Й“e so'aa-aanndude"
  16,27,"Refti Г‘alnde Darngal, O hoynoyayЙ“e, O wi'anaЙ“e: Ko honto kafidaaЙ—i am Й—in Й—i haЙ“iraynoЙ—on fii mun?\" ЖҒen okkaaЙ“e ganndal wi'a: \"Koyeera on hannde e bone on wonii e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  16,28,"ЖҒen Й“en Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hunnata, tooГұuЙ“e ko'e-mun, Й“e werloo jebbilraare, (Й“e wi'a): \"Men wonaa- no gollatnooЙ“e ko boni!\" -\"Wonaa non woniri, pellet Alla ko annduЙ—o ko huuwaynoЙ—on"
  16,29,Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en luttugol ton. Nge bonii ГұaaЖҙorde wonande townitiiЙ“e Й“en
  16,30,"Wi'anee Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e: \"Ko honЙ—um Joomi mon jippini?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Ko moЖҙЖҙere\". Hino woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere; pellet ko saare laakara nden Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude. Nde moЖҙЖҙii saare gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  16,31,"Aljannaaji duumal, hiЙ“e naati Й—i, canЙ—i no ila ley majji. Hino woodani Й“e ton kala ko Й“e faaletee; ko wano nii Alla yoЙ“irta gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  16,32,"ЖҒen Й“e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en warta hara ko Й“e laaЙ“uЙ“e- Й“e wi'an [Й“en]: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon! Naatiree Aljanna on, sabu ko gollaynoЙ—on kon"
  16,33,"Hara [Й“ee sirkooЙ“e fenna] hino habbitii si wanaa nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en arata e maЙ“Й“e, maa yami- roore Joomi maa nden ara? Ko wano non Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e waЙ—irnoo. Alla tooГұaali Й“e; si ko woni, ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wonunoo e tooГұuЙ“e"
  16,34,"Boneeji Й—i Й“e huuwi Й—in memi Й“en, kon ko Й“e jalkitaynoo jippii e maЙ“Й“e"